manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Build Bouquet Flower Arrangement Playset Flower garden building toys for girls have various designs and bright colors, a total of 224 pieces for your little girl to freely match, and a beautiful garden can be created through the assembly. The lilies, daisies, morning glory, plum blossom, orchid, hibiscus and murraya paniculata easy-to-stack in the assorted stems for limitless fun that blossoms in all seasons. It is not only building toys for kids ages 3-6, but also it can be used for room decoration.

Idea Gift for Boys and Girl Children freely combine this flower garden building toy to exercise their imagination, motor skills and learn color discrimination. Whether the kids are on the beach, in the yard or in the classroom, they can build a beautiful garden just as they can imagine! Features: 224 pieces 18 different shapes & 8 different colours All parts are interchangeable Sturdy & easy to stack Easy to clean Smooth Polishing and no sharp edges Can be sterilised through high temperatures before or after use.

100% BPA Free BPA-free & without coating. All parts are made of high-quality, harmless and non-toxic PP plastic. Portable Storage All accessories are put into the storage box. The thoughtful storage box also makes it easy for you to take this garden toy to play outdoors, making it easy to carry and organize. Color Recognition Skills Flower Garden building accessories of different colors can be combined into garden ornaments of different colors to build your own garden.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Flowers blooming everywhere!
reviews.reviewText: This is one of the BEST toys I have purchased for my Kindergarten classroom! The children LOVE these flowers and making a new garden everyday. I purchased a second set for my granddaughters, who also love them! There are so many fun pieces to make it pop! The pieces are very solid quality, not cheap plastic. I highly recommend this fun and creative toy for any child ages 4-8.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful but fragile
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I was so excited to play with these with my kiddos but was very disappointed when I found one of them broken in the packaging and then as we were disassembling them to clean up a green stem with leaves snapped off in my hand. The colors are beautiful and vibrant, and the cute bugs add a fun touch. There are so many different ways to put the track and flowers together making it exciting each time it’s pulled out. It definitely has some small choking hazard parts if you have babies in your home but my 5 year old loves it. Just wish it wasn’t so brittle.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great for my 3yr olds, beware of snapping pieces.
reviews.reviewText: My 3yr olds were gifted this for Christmas, and absolutely love it! It is definitely something we all play together and comes with plenty of pieces for two kids. I would just caution buyers that the leaves do snap off easily if stepped on or caught on carpet when sweeping them into a pile for cleanup. This doesn't bother us, but we do stay on top of any broken pieces to avoid choking hazard.
